snippet.title: Zenodyne R Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Zenodyne R is a 90s shmup inspired by the early 90s shmups, where they were more about awesome FM music and simple reflex-based gameplay. Get it now because it's out!

Features:
- 5 Ships
- 6 Stages
- Multiple Endings
- Tons of unlockable content!

You can purchase the game here:
https://jackdarx.itch.io/zenodyne-r (DRM Free!)
http://store.steampowered.com/app/466820/

You can purchase the soundtrack here:
https://heavyviper.bandcamp.com/album/zenodyne-r-original-soundtrack
Steam link coming soon
